Motherfucker
[[Image:BruceWillis.jpg|thumb|right|"Yippe-ki-yay, motherfucker."]]

'''Motherfucker''' is a classic [[:Category:Epithets|witticism]] that combines the [[clever]] jab of "[[Your mom]]" with the follow up punch of accused [[incest]]. Almost always used by one male to another and often followed by threats of [[violence]].

Contrary to [[popular belief]], only complete [[loser]]s add a smiling [[emoticon]] to a statement that calls an opponent a motherfucker.

Motherfucker is often [[censored]] in [[movies]], [[television]] and [[music]] as "mother-lover", "mother[bleep]", "Mofo", "monkey fighter" or "[[rap|motherkcufer]]"; in print, as "motherf*cker", "motherf***er"; in [[Christian]] [[Bible|literature]] as "**********".

== International Motherfuckers ==
Motherfucker has been a popular epithet for so long that it is one of the three English phrases most likely to be known by foreigners. The other two are "I want a Coca-Cola" and "I surrender."
*'''Italian''': "[Sei un] figlio di puttana" ([You are a] motherfucker).
*[http://zhurnal.lib.ru/k/kabakchi_s_w/finalsolutio444.shtml Russian] "Ну ему сфинкс и говорит: разгадай загадку - пущу тебя к Единому Хранилищу Всей Информации. Разгадал. ЕХВИ ему и говорит. You are a motherfucker"
*'''Brazilian''': "Seu filho da puta" (You motherfucker).
*[http://encyclopediadramatica.com/Faggot French]: "(Tu es un) enfant de chienne" ((You are a) motherfucker).
*'''Quebecer''': "Osti d'enfant d'chienne" (Fucking motherfucker).

